<% front_end_url = ENV.fetch("FRONTEND_URL", "http://localhost:5173") %>
<p>Hello <%= @resource.first_name.presence || @resource.email %>,</p>

<p>Thank you for signing up for Page Chat! We're excited to have you join our community.</p>

<p>To complete your registration and activate your account, please click the link below:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= "#{front_end_url}/activate-account?confirmation_token=#{@token}&email=#{ERB::Util.url_encode(@resource.email)}" %>">
    Activate Your Account
  </a>
</p>

<p>If the link doesn't work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p><%= "#{front_end_url}/activate-account?confirmation_token=#{@token}&email=#{ERB::Util.url_encode(@resource.email)}" %></p>

<p>This link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons.</p>

<p>If you didn't create an account with Page Chat, please ignore this email.</p>

